BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 637.75 Td (Stable flight requires constant adjustment.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 599.08 Td (A drone must control roll, pitch, yaw, and altitude. Roll tilts the drone left or right.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 584.90 Td (Pitch tilts it forward or backward. Yaw rotates it around its vertical axis. Altitude) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 570.73 Td (controls height.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 532.05 Td (The flight controller compares the desired state with the actual state, then adjusts motor) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 517.88 Td (speeds to reduce the error.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 479.20 Td (This is a practical example of feedback control.) Tj ET
