BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 354.45 Td (A simple model might describe how a drone's altitude changes when motor thrust changes. A) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 340.28 Td (more advanced model may use differential equations and state variables to describe motion) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 326.10 Td (over time.) Tj ET
