BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 187.18 Td (A PID controller uses proportional, integral, and derivative terms.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 148.50 Td (The proportional term responds to present error. The integral term responds to accumulated) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 134.33 Td (error. The derivative term responds to the rate of change.) Tj ET
